      "translationId": "peshitta",
      "bookSlug": "john",
      "chapterNumber": 5,
      "verseNumber": 35,
      "referenceLabel": "John 5:35",
      "text": "ܗܘ ܫܪܓܐ ܗܘܐ ܕܕܠܩ ܘܡܢܗܪ ܘܐܢܬܘܢ ܨܒܝܬܘܢ ܕܬܫܬܒܗܪܘܢ ܕܫܥܬܐ ܒܢܘܗܪܗ ܀",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "peshitta:john.5.36",
      "translationId": "peshitta",
      "bookSlug": "john",
      "chapterNumber": 5,
      "verseNumber": 36,
